<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='283000' id='t-283000'>Right. So the next thing is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='285000' id='t-285000'>now why should we get a little bit more active on this?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='287000' id='t-287000'>And the fundamental answer is that</span>
